name: Throwthetrash
0:
”Alexa, open Throw the trash”
”Alexa, ask Throw the trash who should take out the trash”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: throw the trash
des: Next time you're trying to decide whose turn it is pick something or perform a task, just ask Alexa for help. For example, if you're trying to decide whose turn it is to throw the trash, Alexa can randomly select someone's name from the list.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
